---
title: Stir-Fried Hoisin Diced Chicken Breast Noodles with Pepper, Mangetout and Cashews
description: .This Stir-Fried Hoisin Diced Chicken Breast Noodles is a crowd pleaser and is one to get the family round the dinner table for. Super simple to make, and easily customised to suit the kids too.
